high_descs: walk into the kitchen and approach the stove
pick up the pan sitting on the front left coil of the stove
take the pan over to the refrigerator
put the pan in the fridge, close the doors, wait a few moments, then take it back out
take the cooled pan pack over to the stove
put the pan on the back left coil of the stove
anns.task_desc: take a pan from the stove, cool it in the fridge, then put it back on the stove on the back burner.

high_descs: Turn to your right move forward then turn left head to the stove
Pick up the pan on the stove
Turn to your left then move forward turn right to the fridge
Open the fridge put in the pan then take it out and close the fridge
Turn to your left then head to the stove
Put the pan on the far left side of the stove
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled pan on the stove

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the stove on the left.
Pick up the pan on the front left burner.
Walk to the fridge on the right.
Open the fridge door, place the pan on the top shelf, close the door and let the pan chill for a few seconds, take the pan out of the fridge, and close the door.
Turn and walk to the stove on the left.
Place the pan down on the stove on the back left burner.
anns.task_desc: Chill a pan in the fridge and place on the stove.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the oven on your left.
Pick up the pan from on the top of the oven.
Turn and walk to the refrigerator on the same side.
Open the fridge and place the pan in it then close the fridge and after a moment open it and take the pan out and close the fridge again.
Turn walk back to the stove.
Place the pan on the back left burner in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Grab a pan off the stove, put it in the fridge, finally return it back to the stove.

high_descs: Turn around and head towards the stove on your left.
Pick up the black pan on top of the stove on the front, left side.
Turn left, head towards the dining table and hang a right towards the white fridge.
Open the fridge doors, place the pan on the upper right shelf, close the doors to let the pan get cold for a moment, then open the doors, retrieve the pan from inside, and close the doors.
Turn around to face the door, turn left, cross the room and turn left when you reach the stove.
Put the pan down on the top of the stove in back left corner next to the big black pot.
anns.task_desc: Place a cold pan on the stove.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the stove.
Pick up the pan from the left side of the stove,
Turn around and walk to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator and put the pan inside then close the refrigerator door. Wait a few seconds then open the refrigerator and take the pan out. Close the door.
Turn around and walk back to the stove.
Put the pan on the back of the stove top.
anns.task_desc: Cool down the pan on the left side of the stove.
